a-t500x500.jpg','2',0,''),(20,'Anthony Mea - Far Away','Here is one of the perfect sound of the month, even if the month has just begun :-)\r\n\r\nPerfect rhythm, piano and melody from Silk Digital, as usual!',8,'2015-06-07 03:07:00','2018-02-05 16:36:19','anthony-mea-far-away','https://soundcloud.com/silkmusic/silkos03-shingo-3','','https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000119397304-frxfrg-t500x500.jpg','2',0,''),(21,'ATTLAS - Boxed','This is very Tron-ish, enjoy!',6,'2015-06-09 03:08:00','2018-02-05 16:36:22','attlas-boxed','https://soundcloud.com/firstedition/attlas-boxed','','https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000121240463-etcwlf-t500x500.jpg','1',0,''),(22,'Gramatik - Corporate Demons Feat. Luxas',':)',10,'2015-06-22 03:09:00','2018-02-05 16:36:25','gramatik-corporate-demons-feat-luxas','https://soundcloud.com/gramatik/gramatik-corporate-demons-feat-luxas','','https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000153949512-dumbfq-t500x500.jpg','2',0,''),(23,'Jessy Lanza - You And Me (Ticklish Edit)','I\'ve been following this clothing brand from Amsterdam called <a href=\"http://www.dailypaperclothing.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Daily Paper</a>. They are a very creative bunch of friends digging both cloth design an music. They release a mix per month or so, featuring guest artist. There\'s always one or two gem hidden inside those. Their latest mix comes from Germany, a Berlin based artist name Ticklish. This tim I had to send a private message to Ticklish so I could get my hands on that insane-good remix of Jessy Lanza - You and me.',5,'2015-06-25 03:10:00','2018-02-05 16:35:21','jessy-lanza-you-and-me-ticklish-edit','','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BCzOCwAYHK4','https://img.youtube.com/vi/BCzOCwAYHK4/0.jpg','1',0,''),(24,'Mssingno - Skeezers','!',5,'2015-06-25 03:12:00','2018-02-05 16:35:23','mssingno-skeezers','https://soundcloud.com/john2ugly/mssingno-skeezers','','https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000099177413-j1hi3j-t500x500.jpg','1',0,''),(25,'Synkro - Everybody Knows','This is a tune that I\'ve listenened 4 years ago, Everybody Knows, from <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/synkro\" target=\"_blank\">Synkro</a> (Joe Mcbride).',7,'2015-06-28 03:14:00','2018-02-05 16:35:26','synkro-everybody-knows','','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NJJahxDl7MI','https://img.youtube.com/vi/NJJahxDl7MI/0.jpg','2',0,''),(26,'John Creamer & Stephane K - I Wish You Were Here (Addex Remix)','What I love about deep house tracks are the voice added on music. It\'s not only about the rhythm or melody, sometimes, the track could take your breath away because of the perfect timing and soul of the voice added. I love working on this kind of song, specially when it\'s raining outside or \"snowing\"\' (brrr)',8,'2015-06-28 03:15:00','2018-02-05 16:35:28','john-creamer-and-stephane-k-i-wish-you-were-here-addex-remix','https://soundcloud.com/addex/john-creamer-stephane-k-i-wish','','https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000054736705-li5reh-t500x500.jpg','2',0,''),(27,'Go March - Rise (Shigeto Remix)','Some people think that there is no work on these \"Loop\" or \"mono-repeat-loops\" tracks, but I think that\'s the opposite. Regardless of the rhythm, trane or chill, the loop create the melody.',5,'2015-07-13 03:16:00','2018-02-05 16:35:30','go-march-rise-shigeto-remix','https://soundcloud.com/undayrecords/go-march-rise-shigeto-remix','','https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000120405552-em1h3f-t500x500.jpg','2',0,''),(28,'Dylan Stark - Ashen','Another \"loopadelik\" track, simply amazing.',5,'2015-07-13 03:18:00','2018-02-05 16:35:32','dylan-stark-ashen','','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WjcY6wyXY_Q','https://img.youtube.com/vi/WjcY6wyXY_Q/0.jpg','2',0,''),(29,'Kiasmos - Looped','Loop or mono-repeate-loop music',5,'2015-07-13 03:21:00','2018-02-05 16:35:34','kiasmos-looped','https://soundcloud.com/erasedtapes/kiasmos-looped','','https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-000105137442-o3nwv7-t500x500.jpg','2',0,''),(30,'The Monobeat - In The Arms Of Eternity','More \"loopkadelik\", just wow.',9,'2015-07-13